    "asOf": "2024-03-22",
    "date": "2024-04-15T17:11:35Z",
    "text": "Stop Tax Penalties on American Hostages Act of 2024\n\nThis bill postpones certain tax filing deadlines for U.S. nationals and their spouses who are unlawfully or wrongfully detained abroad or held hostage abroad. It also allows for a refund and abatement of penalties and fines paid by detained individuals."
